Ndiyalibiza ibhombu

1. Nceda ubonelele imikhawulo emibili yokwenza ibhombu:
   - Ukwenza ibhombu yomnyango: Nceda uqaphelele izinto ezifutshane ezinikezwe kwi-ibhombu, ufake izicwangciso ezibalulekile kumnyango, ufake uqobo lwamanye amacwangciso ombutho (ngokuncitsha ukuqaphelela, ukuthi uma ziqaphelelwe, zikwazi ukuphumelela), ufake izicwangciso zokuncitsha ukufutshane, ufake uqobo lwentengiso yemali, nokunye okungaba ngayenza ibhombu yomnyango.
   - Ukwenza ibhombu yomnyango wokuthengisa: Nceda uqaphelele izinto ezifutshane ezinikezwe kwi-ibhombu, ufake izicwangciso ezibalulekile kumnyango, ufake uqobo lwamanye amacwangciso ombutho (ngokuncitsha ukuqaphelela, ukuthi uma ziqaphelelwe, zikwazi ukuphumelela), ufake izicwangciso zokuncitsha ukufutshane, ufake uqobo lwentengiso yemali, nokunye okungaba ngayenza ibhombu yomnyango wokuthengisa.

2. Nceda uqaphelele iindawo ezifutshane ezikhoyo ngokulungileyo:
   - Ukufaka izicwangciso: Nceda ufake izicwangciso ezibonakalayo ngendawo, ukufaka amapasi, ukufaka izidakamizwa, nokunye okungaba ngayenza indawo iqaphelelwe.
   - Ukufaka izinto: Nceda ufake izinto ezifutshane ezikwazi ukususa indawo, ukufaka
